title: Pix2ASCII
description: Pix2ASCII Art Studio is an AI-powered web app that turns images into high-quality ASCII art using React 19, Vite 6, and Google Gemini 1.5 Flash. It offers real-time rendering, multiple styles, color support, and high-resolution exports with a modern retro-terminal aesthetic.

title: ExeKiller-v1.1
description: ExeKiller is a lightweight Windows tool that forcefully terminates active programming environments like Python, C#, Java, Node.js, and C++. It features an interactive menu, fast native performance, and zero external dependenciesideal for quick development environment resets.

title: PORT-Controller
description: Port Controller by OSAMA is a Windows CLI tool for monitoring active ports and managing local processes. It lets you find which app is using a port and safely terminate it, with admin checks and built-in system protections.

title: QuizMaster bot
description: Quiz Master is a smart and interactive quiz bot designed to challenge your knowledge, sharpen your mind, and make learning fun. From quick trivia to competitive challenges, it offers engaging quizzes, instant scoring, and a dynamic way to test your brain anytime.

title: LTQR
description: Link-to-QR is a simple online tool that lets you convert any web link into a scannable QR code in seconds  just paste your URL and generate a QR image you can download or share.
